channel.title: Port-forward? (forgot router name + pw) pls help!
channel.description:
Hi Guys , i got my Client ( 508 ) nd source. I run source , i change ip from client to my own. I can play it , but other peoples cant. It says error conencting to server. I need to portforward, but ill forgot my Router name & Password :( [b]Its a Netopia 7000 Router. Ill already try usenrame : admin password : 1234 , etc[/b] but it is wrong :S [size=10pt][b]Im from switzerland [/b][/size], can any1 help me how to find out my router name and pw XD?
Thanks :(

item.dc:creator: @Jammydee Jammydee
item.description:
@Jammydee wrote:

If all else fails and you cannot find the password at all, there is a reset button on your router, but you’ll need to re-enter all of your settings etc… this will change the password back to the default (it should say the default username + password on the router itself)

However… Only do this if your confident in your ability to set the router back up! Else you’ll be without internet and help…
